pageContext.claim: “They do a poll -- I was at 88 percent, and now I'm at, you know, very low number -- in Europe. I don't care about Europe.”
pageContext.analysis: It's unclear what poll Trump is referring to, and we didn't find anything close to 88 percent approval or support for Trump among Europeans. Polls by the Pew Research Center in 2017 and 2018 have found low support for Trump among Europeans.
